sarea unto me.","year":41},{"id":"recjADe4lp6zuRM3s","ref":"Acts.12.19","text":"And when Herod had sought for him, and found him not, he examined the keepers, and commanded that they should be put to death. And he went down from Judaea to Caesarea, and there abode.","year":44},{"id":"rec9iKGE0acfvmfB0","ref":"Acts.18.22","text":"And when he had landed at Caesarea, and gone up, and saluted the church, he went down to Antioch.","year":54},{"id":"recGBlhN3XQg1Vea1","ref":"Acts.21.8","text":"And the next day we that were of Paul’s company departed, and came unto Caesarea: and we entered into the house of Philip the evangelist, which was one of the seven; and abode with him.","year":60}]}
